# Ability Name	Unique Key				Category of Ability		Type															Multiple Requirements																					Innate Spells											Description																																																																											Bonus to DC				Bonus to skill					Natural Attacks
Change Shape	KEY:Change Shape ~ Kitsune	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.KitsuneRacialTrait.KitsuneRacialDefault	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Change Shape ~ Kitsune],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.KitsuneChangeShape]															DESC:A kitsune can assume the appearance of a single human form of the same sex,this form is static, and cannot be changed each time the kitsune assumes this form. A kitsune in human form cannot make its bite attack, but gains a +10 racial bonus on Disguise checks made to appear human. Changing from human to kitsune shape is a standard action. This ability otherwise functions as alter self, save that the kitsune does not adjust its ability scores.
Agile			KEY:Agile ~ Kitsune		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.KitsuneRacialTrait.KitsuneRacialDefault	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Agile ~ Kitsune],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.KitsuneAgile]																	DESC:Kitsune receive a +2 racial bonus on Acrobatics checks.																																																																							BONUS:SKILL|Acrobatics|2|TYPE=Racial
Kitsune Magic	KEY:Kitsune Magic ~ Kitsune	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.SpellLike.KitsuneRacialTrait.KitsuneRacialDefault		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Kitsune Magic ~ Kitsune],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.KitsuneMagic]		SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=3|CASTERLEVEL=TL|Dancing Lights,10+CHA|PRESTAT:1,CHA=11	DESC:Kitsune add +1 to the DC of any saving throws against enchantment spells that they cast. Kitsune with a Charisma of 11 or higher also gain a spell-like ability.																																																	BONUS:DC|SCHOOL.Enchantment|1
Natural Weapon	KEY:Natural Weapon ~ Kitsune	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.KitsuneRacialTrait.KitsuneRacialDefault	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Natural Weapon ~ Kitsune],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.KitsuneNaturalWeapon]														DESC:A kitsune has a bite attack in its natural form. This bite does a base of 1d4 points of damage on a hit. This is a primary attack, or a secondary attack if the kitsune wields a manufactured weapon.																																																							NATURALATTACKS:Bite,Weapon.Natural.Melee.Finesseable.Piercing.Slashing,*1,1d4

